MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2010-0543. Coon v. Technical Constr. Specialties, Inc.

Summit App. No. 24542, 2010-Ohio-417. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
